      <p>In 2014 I launched a web product called DesignMeetsBeats, which was essentially Crew.co for the music industry, in an attempt to help early-career musicians build stronger visual brands.</p><p> After experimenting with two business models, it became clear that in order to truly move the needle for artists, I needed a.) more control and b.) a more direct and robust revenue engine that would scale as musicians scaled their following.</p>
    </div>
