      <h2>The Customer</h2>
      <h3>Electronic Musicians with following (f) 1000 < (f) < 10000 across all channels.</h3>
      <p>Building an artist career in music today is radically different from doing it 30 years ago. Audience critical mass is about 10,000 active followers to support one team member with regular monetization like pay-what-you-want albums paired with premium offerings for superfans.</p>
      <p>This has given rise to a thriving ecosystem of monetized properties promoting, developing, releasing, and consuming music online, all of which feeds into the offline world of live shows and merch sales.</p>
      <p>The artists involved and the people behind these properties are Mocktail's clients.</p>
