      <h2>The Product(-ized Service)</h2>
      <p>Mocktail makes thoughtful visual identities and graphic art, delivered  professionally and consistently.</p>
      <h3>The Value</h3>
      <p></p>Customers use these visual identities when working with promoters, agents, and labels to book shows and produce promotional material. The music industry is obsessed with branding to a degree that makes tech companies look like weekend warriors, so having design materials that pass the “sniff test” can be crucial when starting an artist career.
      </p>
